    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An island made of candy sounds like paradise – but for the residents of Sarkara, fabled to be the home of the legendary Serenity Sweet, devastating earthquakes are threatening the resident’s idyllic way of life! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >YOU are an investigator sent to Sarkara to uncover what’s threatening the island – and all of reality as we know it.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ~ ~ Dress up in found objects. Reinvent yourself! ~ ~ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have lost all your stuff in a disastrous crash. Re-equip yourself with any item you find, from a doll’s lost arm to a floaty feather. All can affect your dialogue skill checks and minigame moves. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269360/extras/07b34ab87ef7b902431c9aa1f95df3ac.poster.avif?t=1758676154\" width=476 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269360/extras/07b34ab87ef7b902431c9aa1f95df3ac.webm?t=1758676154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269360/extras/07b34ab87ef7b902431c9aa1f95df3ac.mp4?t=1758676154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ~ ~ Make friends with weirdos ~ ~ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get involved in local politics – or maybe accidentally join a cult. You'll have to form alliances and make enemies to get to the bottom of the mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269360/extras/931d7c91835d3ad705448c8c433b9e31.poster.avif?t=1758676154\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269360/extras/931d7c91835d3ad705448c8c433b9e31.webm?t=1758676154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269360/extras/931d7c91835d3ad705448c8c433b9e31.mp4?t=1758676154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ~ ~ Get into various altercations ~ ~ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When dialogue is not enough, settle disputes in minigames. Find limbs and candy that grant special moves to sway conflict in your favor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269360/extras/8aab65fbfe2a3e6eeaf9c7dc1d50d0f8.poster.avif?t=1758676154\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269360/extras/8aab65fbfe2a3e6eeaf9c7dc1d50d0f8.webm?t=1758676154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269360/extras/8aab65fbfe2a3e6eeaf9c7dc1d50d0f8.mp4?t=1758676154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ~ ~ Roll through some delicious sweet locations ~ ~ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more you uncover while exploring Sarkara Island, the more mysteries you unlock: what’s causing the devastating earthquakes? Who is the other O.H.N.O. official that has been sent to the island? And could the mythical Serenity Sweet, which everyone claims can make your dreams come true, really be somewhere on the island?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
